query:
INSERT INTO
            achievements(id, series, tag, name, description, jades, hidden)
        VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
        ON CONFLICT
            (id)
        DO UPDATE SET
        series = EXCLUDED.series,
            tag = EXCLUDED.tag,
            name = EXCLUDED.name,
            description = EXCLUDED.description,
            jades = EXCLUDED.jades,
            hidden = EXCLUDED.hidden
